original_title: Looney Tunes Super Stars Tweety & Sylvester: Feline Fwenzy
overview: It's not your imagination; you really "taw a puddy tat." Laugh your way through 15 bird-chasing, all-time cartoon favorites with "Looney Tunes Super Stars: Tweety & Sylvester." It's a grand collection featuring the clever canary and the cagey cat. Includes classic Warner Bros. cartoons like "The Last Hungry Cat," "Snow Business," "Birds Anonymous" and the Oscar-winning short "Tweetie Pie."
title: Looney Tunes Super Stars Tweety & Sylvester: Feline Fwenzy
